Name: Meowlux Mystery Box
Description: Open to receive a Meowlux Wish Coin and randomly get a toy. Use the Wish Coin to participate in the Wish for a chance to get exclusive appearances, mounts, as well as Meowlux Premium Card, Meowlux Vault Card, dye materials, toys, and many other rewards.
